		{"id":"n1","type":"text","text":"Trellis + Superpowers 模板","x":-1080,"y":-120,"width":320,"height":120},
		{"id":"n2","type":"text","text":"1) 创建 fixture 项目\npython3 scripts/create_fixture_project.py /tmp/ts-demo","x":-680,"y":-280,"width":380,"height":150},
		{"id":"n3","type":"text","text":"2) 安装模板\npython3 scripts/install_template.py --target /tmp/ts-demo --developer <name> --platform codex --platform claude","x":-220,"y":-280,"width":460,"height":170},
		{"id":"n4","type":"text","text":"3) 验证\npython3 scripts/validate_template.py --mode quick","x":320,"y":-280,"width":360,"height":140},
		{"id":"n5","type":"text","text":"quick 通过？","x":760,"y":-280,"width":200,"height":120},
		{"id":"n6","type":"text","text":"可以投入使用\n在目标仓库用 codex/claude 执行 strict-dev-workflow","x":1040,"y":-440,"width":360,"height":140},
		{"id":"n7","type":"text","text":"失败分支（当前仓库实测）\n2026-03-15: Trellis pin commit checkout 失败\nfatal: unable to read tree ...","x":1040,"y":-120,"width":420,"height":170},
		{"id":"n8","type":"text","text":"修复后重试\nA. 更新 versions.lock.json 的 trellis commit\nB. 或调整 clone 逻辑支持检出 pin commit","x":1520,"y":-120,"width":420,"height":170},
		{"id":"n9","type":"text","text":"工作流执行阶段\nPRD -> Diagnose -> Plan -> Execute(TDD) -> Verify -> Commit -> Record","x":1040,"y":-640,"width":520,"height":150},
